name: Alex Martinez
content:
#Booksmart dir. Olivia Wilde

-Absolutely hilarious, led by likable leads and a great script.
-Strong supporting cast, mainly Billie Lourd and Skyler Gisondo.
-Well paced, a simple yet engaging story.
-One of the best comedies in recent years.
-A terrific debut for Wilde.

content: #Booksmart manages to tick the box on every teen movie “coming of age” “one last night out” trope but never falls into cliché. There’s no overtly mean bully or superjock. Their classmates aren’t real nemeses, they’re actually cool kids separated by their interests/differences.

name: Coming Off The Reels
